Dataset
The project uses the ML-ArXiv-Papers dataset from Hugging Face.
Dataset includes approximately:

15,000 Machine Learning research papers
Title
Abstract
Each paper is converted into embeddings and indexed inside FAISS for semantic retrieval.
Project Workflow
Step 1
Load the research paper dataset.
Step 2
Combine the title and abstract into a single searchable document.
Step 3
Generate dense embeddings using Sentence Transformers.
Step 4
Store embeddings inside a FAISS vector database.
Step 5
Convert the user's query into an embedding.
Step 6
Retrieve the most semantically similar papers.
Step 7
Generate concise summaries using the BART summarization model.
Step 8
Extract important keywords using KeyBERT.
Step 9
Generate an AI-powered research profile including:
Research Area
Method
Dataset
Task
Contribution
Difficulty Level
Best Suited Audience
Estimated Reading Time
Step 10
Present the final ranked research recommendations.
