Installation
git clone https://github.com/Fiza-1300/Research_paper_intelligence_system.git

cd Research_paper_intelligence_system
Create a virtual environment:
python -m venv venv
Activate it:
Linux/macOS

source venv/bin/activate
Windows
venv\Scripts\activate
Install dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt
Usage
Run the main application:
python app.py
Example query:
Find the top 5 research papers on Vision Transformers.
The system will:
Retrieve the most relevant papers
Generate summaries
Extract keywords
Create structured AI research profiles
Display ranked recommendations
